quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  21,11,aur hum ne bohat si bustiyon ko jo sitamgar theen halaak kar mara aur un ke baad aur log peda kardiye
  21,12,jab unhon ne hamaray ( muqadma ) azaab ko dekha to lagey is se bhagnay
  21,13,mat bhago aur jin ( nematon ) mein tum aish o aasaish karte they un ki aur apne gharon ki taraf lout jao. shayad tum se ( is baray mein ) daryaftkiya jaye
  21,14,kehnay lagey haae shamat be shak hum zalim they
  21,15,to woh hamesha isi terhan pkarte rahay yahan taq ke hum ne un ko ( khaiti ki terhan ) kaat kar ( aur aag ki terhan ) bujha kar dhair kardiya
  21,16,aur hum ne aasman aur zameen ko jo aur ( makhloqaat ) un dono ke darmain hai is ko لہوولعب ke liye peda nahikiya
  21,17,agar hum chahtay ke khail ( ki cheezein yani zan o farzand ) banayen to agar hum ko karna hota to hum apne paas se bnalite
  21,18,balkay hum sach ko jhoot par khech maartay hain to woh is ka sir toar deta hai aur jhoot isi waqt nabood hojata hai. aur jo baatein tum banatay ho un se tumhari hi kharabi hai
  21,19,aur jo log asmano mein aur jo zameen mein hain sab isi ke ( mamlook aur usi ka maal hain. aur jo ( farishtay ) uss ke paas hain woh is ki ibadat se nah kunyatay(nah sarkashi kartay hain ) hain aur nah uktatay hain
  21,20,raat din ( uss ki ) tasbeeh karte rehtay hain ( nah thakte hain ) nah uktatay hain
  21,21,bhala logon ne jo zameen ki cheezon se ( baaz ko ) mabood bana liya hai ( tokiya ) woh un ko ( marnay ke baad ) uttha khara karen ge ?
  21,22,agar aasman aur zameen mein khuda ke siwa aur mabood hotay to zameen o asmaan darham barham ho jatay. jo baatein yeh log batatay hain khuday-e maalik arsh un se pak hai
  21,23,woh jo kaam karta hai is ki parastish nahi hogi aur ( jo kaam yeh log karte hain is ki ) un se parastish hogi
  21,24,kiya logon ne khuda ko chore kar aur mabood bnalye hain. keh do ke ( is baat par ) apni Daleel paish karo. yeh ( meri aur ) mere sath walon ki kitaab bhi hai aur jo mujh se pehlay ( paighambar ) hue hain. un ki kitaaben bhi hain. balkay ( baat yeh hai ke ) un aksar haq baat ko nahi jantay aur is liye is se munh phair letay hain
